data.revised_prompt: Envisage a high-quality, mouthwatering image of a 'Smoky Spiced Velvet' cocktail. This cocktail is a mix of 1.5 oz mezcal, 1 oz silky coconut milk, 0.5 oz honey syrup, 0.5 oz fresh lime juice, 2 dashes of chili bitters, decorated with 3 fresh basil leaves and a sprinkle of smoked paprika. A well-lit scene showcases the cocktail placed in an appropriate glass with meticulous garnishes. The image should look ultra-realistic and appealing, resembling a photograph taken by a professional food photographer. The backdrop is crystal clear with gentle blur. No text or watermarks present and the overall style is photorealistic.
